<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202972>
    bibo:endPage "22" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "1" ;
    bibo:volume "2734" ;
    dc:creator "Anker, Arthur" ;
    dc:date "2011" ;
    dc:title "Four new infaunal decapod crustaceans (Caridea: Alpheidae and Gebiidea: Axianassidae) from Lizard Island, Australia, one of them also occurring in Moorea, French Polynesia" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202973>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202974>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202980> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202973>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Athanas shawnsmithi n. sp., allotype, male from Lizard Island, Australia (QM W 29046): A, frontal region, dorsal; B, same, lateral; C, carapace, lateral; D, third maxilliped, lateral; E, appendix masculina and appendix interna of second pleopod; F, articulated flap on sixth abdominal somite, lateral; G, uropod, dorsal; H, telson, dorsal; I, same, detail of posterior margin (plumose setae omitted)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/202973/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202974>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Athanas shawnsmithi n. sp., allotype, male from Lizard Island, Australia (QM W 29046) [A – D, F – I]; holotype, ovigerous female from Lizard Island (QM W 29045) [E]: A, major cheliped, lateral; B, same, mesial; C, same, chela, mesial (extensor view); D, same, fingers open, lateral (flexor view); E, minor cheliped, lateral; F, second pereiopod, lateral; G, third pereiopod, lateral; H, same, distal propodus and dactylus; I, fifth pereiopod, lateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/202974/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202980>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Habitus and colour patterns of Athanas shawnsmithi n. sp. [A – D], Athanas daviei n. sp. [E, F], and Athanopsis saurus n. sp. [G, H], all from Lizard Island, Australia: A, B, allotype, male (QM W 29046), lateral and dorsal; C, D, holotype, female (QM W 29045), lateral and dorsal; E, F, holotype male (QM W 29047), lateral and dorsal; G, H, holotype, male (QM W 29048), lateral and dorsal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/202980/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

